sections.text: Transfer of Powers and Duties of State Exposition and Fairgrounds Office and of the Director of the Department of Natural Resources and the Department of Natural Resources Under the Michigan Exposition and Fairgrounds Act From the Office of Director, Department of Natural Resources, to the Director of the Department of Commerce; Transfer of the State Exposition and Fairgrounds Council to the Department of Commerce by a Type II Transfer.
